---
description: UI system rules
globs:
  - "src/**/*.jsx"
  - "src/**/*.js"
alwaysApply: false
---

Use the MUI theme in `src/theme/theme.js` for colors, spacing, typography, radii, and component defaults.

Do not add arbitrary colors, spacing values, decorative gradients, glass effects, or emoji icons.

Every screen should have one clear primary action.

